review:
∞ Infinitely replayable Air-Ships/Fighter jets/Intense Dog-Fights, on like extra-terrestrial planets, fighting Death Star systems, or like cruisers, but Homeworld destroyer types and you're just this puny jet that eventually becomes a flying tank.

 Great with keyboard and mouse. Steam controller was not easy to get comfortable with. You want precision, maybe I must try a different config, if anyone can recommend one by name. 
Excellent game otherwise. SHMUP lite, but you can go far if you are determined.

There are daily challenges - and leaderboards for them; 
Airborne upgrades. Always flying once you lift-off;
